{"type": "article", "id": 6004, "title": "宜家 Sinnerlig 系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-09T07:34:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233926E34F1bYSVz7BNOcU.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t在今年的斯德哥尔摩家具展上，宜家联手伦敦设计师 Ilse Crawford 推出了 30 余件软木和天然纤维家居产品 Sinnerlig 系列，大到软木茶几，小到手工吹制玻璃瓶，挑选那些适于任何居家环境的中性色彩。Ilse Crawford 表示，Sinnerlig 系列的产品都着重于材料的组合，而非产品的形状。这会是一组在家居环境中非常低调的角色，它不会以抢眼的设计夺人眼球，但却是最令人感到舒服的背景。据 Dezeen 报道，这一系列产品将于今年 8 月登陆宜家商场与线上商店。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233921yWsAUxRLH0grFCMT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3359375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233922NJZFbali08K9ymSo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3359375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233923Q83EqzixnoBPSc9I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3359375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233923ZEHzSW1AKeVubfMP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3359375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233924ogVwNh9idXm75Ybq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}